&lt;h1 id=&#34;covid-19-dashboard&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#covid-19-dashboard&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 🦠 COVID-19 Dashboard ·&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/adamalston/COVID-19-Dashboard&#34;&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://circleci.com/gh/adamalston/COVID-19-Dashboard.svg?style=shield&#34; alt=&#34;Circle CI&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://adamalston.github.io/COVID-19-Dashboard/&#34;&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://img.shields.io/website?down_message=down&amp;amp;label=gh-pages&amp;amp;up_message=passing&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fadamalston.github.io%2FCOVID-19-Dashboard&#34; alt=&#34;Dashboard&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;COVID-19 dashboard and map built with &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ2F0c2J5anMub3JnLw==&#34;&gt;Gatsby&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9yZWFjdC1sZWFmbGV0LmpzLm9yZw==&#34;&gt;React Leaflet&lt;/span&gt;, and &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubWFwYm94LmNvbS8=&#34;&gt;Mapbox&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nootifmemory/COVID19/master/src/assets/images/preview.png&#34; alt=&#34;COVID Map&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This dashboard includes data related to cases, deaths, and testing efforts. Information at a country level is displayed on cards that are activated on hover. Information at a global level (i.e. sum of all data) is displayed at the bottom of the page.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;data&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#data&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 📊 Data&lt;/h2&gt;
